data.title: Analysis of fruit juice by atomic absorption spectrophotometry I.—The determination of iron and tin in canned juice
data.meta_description: Atomic absorption spectrophotometry has been used to compare the concentrations of iron and tin in canned fruit juice with those in juice not stored in cans. No significant difference was found in th...
